    <lb n="1"/><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">Ἀμ</supplied>μώνι<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ος Ἀπίωνι τ</supplied>ῷ ἀ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">δε</supplied>λφῷ χ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">αί</unclear>ρ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ειν</supplied>. 

    <lb n="2"/>πρὸ πάντων ἀσπά<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ζομ</supplied><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">αι</unclear> ὴν ἀδελφὴν καὶ 

    <lb n="3"/><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">τὰ</supplied> <unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">παιδία</unclear> σου πάντα. ἐὰν δύ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">νῃ</supplied> ἐγπλέ-

    <lb n="4"/>ξαι περσικὰ τὰ <supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ἐπ</supplied>ὶ τῆς <unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ἀ</unclear><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">γορ</supplied>ᾶ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ς, μ</supplied>ὴ ἀμελήσῃς 

    <lb n="5"/>ὡς <choice><corr>εἰδὼς</corr><sic>ιδως</sic></choice> ὅτι θεῶν θελόντων ἤδη <choice><corr>μέλλει</corr><sic>μελλι</sic></choice> τὰ 

    <lb n="6"/>ὧδε καταστ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">έ</supplied>λ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">λε</supplied>σθαι καὶ μέλλω καὶ <choice><corr>ἐγὼ</corr><sic>καγω</sic></choice> πρὸς 

    <lb n="7"/><choice><corr>σὲ</corr><sic>σεν</sic></choice> γίνεσθαι. δι<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ὸ</unclear> ὖν μὴ ἀμελήσῃς καὶ 

    <lb n="8"/>εἰς τ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ὴ</supplied>ν <choice><corr>ὠνὴν</corr><sic>ονην</sic></choice> καὶ πα<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ρα</supplied>χρῆμα <choice><corr>σὺ</corr><sic>σ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">οι</unclear></sic></choice> <supplied reason="lost" cert="high">α</supplied>ὐτὰ 

    <lb n="9"/><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ἀ</unclear>γ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ό</unclear>ρασαι. πάντ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ω</supplied>ς οὖ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ν σ</supplied>ὺ πρᾶξον ὡς <choice><corr>εἰδὼς</corr><sic>ιδως</sic></choice> 

    <lb n="10"/><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ὅ</supplied>τι τοῦ θεοῦ <sic>θεοῦ</sic> θέλοντος τάχα καὶ <choice><corr>ἐγὼ</corr><sic>καγω</sic></choice> ἐν 

    <lb n="11"/><choice><corr>τάχει</corr><sic>ταχι</sic></choice> σε <choice><corr>κατέλαβον</corr><sic>κατελα<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">β</supplied>α</sic></choice>. εἶπον δὲ <unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">κ</unclear>α<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ὶ</unclear> τῷ <choice><corr>κωφῷ</corr><sic>κωπω</sic></choice> Δι-

    <lb n="12"/>ονυσίῳ <hi rend="diaeresis">ἵ</hi>να καὶ αὐτὸς ὃ ἐὰν εὕρῃ ἀγοράσῃ. 

    <lb n="13"/>καὶ δι᾽ οὗ ἐὰν εὕρῃς ἐπιστολίδιόν μοι πέμ-

    <lb n="14"/>ψον. ἀλλὰ μὴ ἀμελήσῃς μηδὲ ψυχρεύσῃ 

    <lb n="15"/>τοῦ ὅσα ἐὰν <choice><corr>ἐνῇ</corr><sic>ενην</sic></choice> ἀγοράσαι ὡς <choice><corr>εἰδὼς</corr><sic>ιδως</sic></choice> ὅτι οὐ-

    <lb n="16"/><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">δὲν</supplied> <choice><corr>μέλλεις</corr><sic>μελλις</sic></choice> <choice><corr>εἰς</corr><sic>ις</sic></choice> ἐμὲ <choice><corr>βλάπτεσθαι</corr><sic>βλαπτεσται</sic></choice> ἀλλὰ οὐ-

    <lb n="17"/>δὲ <choice><corr>λυπεῖσθαι</corr><sic>λ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">οι</unclear>πισται</sic></choice>. πάντως οὖν πρ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ᾶγ</unclear>μά σου 

    <lb n="18"/>πρᾶξον <hi rend="diaeresis">ἵ</hi>να <unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">δι</unclear>ὰ σοῦ μόνου τὰ ὄντα <choice><corr>ᾖ</corr><sic>ην</sic></choice> 

    <lb n="19"/><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ἀ</unclear>γ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ο</unclear>ρα<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">σθ</unclear>έντα περσικά. πάντως μὴ ἀ-

    <lb n="20"/>μελήσῃς. ἄσ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">π</supplied>α<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">σ</supplied><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">αι</unclear> Παμμένην καὶ τοὺς 

    <lb n="21"/>αὐτοῦ πάντας. ἐὰν <choice><corr>χρείαν</corr><sic>χριαν</sic></choice> ἔχῃ Διονύσιος ὁ ἀδελ-

    <lb n="22"/>φός μου, ἕως δραχμῶν ἑκατὸν δὸς αὐτῷ καὶ <choice><corr>λα<supplied reason="omitted" cert="high">βὲ</supplied></corr><sic>λα</sic></choice> αὐ-

    <lb n="23"/>τὰς παρ᾽ ἐμοῦ, ἀλλὰ μὴ ἄλλως. 

    <lb n="24"/>ἐρρῶσθαί σε εὔχομαι πανοικὶ μετὰ τοῦ οἴκου 

    <lb n="25"/>σου <unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ὅλου</unclear>, ἄδελφε Ἀπί<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ω</unclear><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ν</supplied>. </ab></div><div n="meta.30783" type="description" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><rs type="material" cert="high">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.30783" type="commentary" subtype="textDate" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><date type="textDate" notBefore="201" notAfter="300">III</date></p></div><div n="meta.30783" type="commentary" subtype="mentionedDates" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><head>Erwähnte Daten</head></div><div n="meta.30783" type="bibliography" subtype="principalEdition" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><listBibl default="NO"><bibl type="publication" subtype="principal" default="NO"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">P.Ross. Georg.</title><biblScope type="volume">3</biblScope><biblScope type="numbers">3</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="Trismegistos" default="NO"><biblScope type="numbers">30783</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="DDbDP" default="NO"><series>0197</series>; <biblScope type="volume">3</biblScope>; <biblScope type="numbers">3</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref type="Perseus" href="0197;3;3" evaluate="all" from="ROOT" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.30783" type="bibliography" subtype="illustrations" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p>keine</p></div><div n="meta.30783" type="bibliography" subtype="otherPublications" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><head>Andere Publikationen</head><listBibl default="NO"><bibl type="publication" subtype="other" default="NO">SB III 7242</bibl><bibl type="publication" subtype="other" default="NO">C.Pap. Hengstl 121</bibl><bibl type="publication" subtype="other" default="NO">Tibiletti, Lettere private 12</bibl></listBibl></div><div n="meta.30783" type="bibliography" subtype="translations" org="uniform" part="N" sample="com